{"tid":1849400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【垃圾人種】支那要求日本提供口罩 唔俾錢屈人係捐贈","createTime":"2020-01-29T04:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T18:16:35.000Z","uid":117837,"like":533,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"f45a23c382993d804d7dd1e335e4b37db30a3137","tid":1849400,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"一宗羅生門事件<br />\n中國政府主動要求<br />\n伊藤洋華堂提供100万個口罩給中國<br />\n同時發動網絡輿論攻勢造成是伊藤洋華堂&ldquo;免費贈送&rdquo;<br />\n要脅伊藤洋華堂免費供應捐贈口罩<br />\n伊藤洋華堂表示從來沒有提過免費贈送的事情<br />\n接到要求時以爲中方是真金白銀購買<br />\n因爲情勢緊急日方寬鬆處理先到貨後付款<br />\n誰知到貨後中方突然變臉稱到貨爲贈品<br />\n伊藤洋華堂現在是相當尷尬<br />\n只能先承諾無論如何會盡力協助災區受害者<br />\n真是厲害了強國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/653010246/posts/10163124352695247/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F653010246%2Fposts%2F10163124352695247%2F&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=14091d04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/653010246/posts/10163124352695247/</a>"},{"pid":"e72cb4022d0cd37d993ae9cba918250aa9bd94cb","tid":1849400,"uid":53062,"like":95,"dislike":6,"score":89,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:49:56.000Z","msg":"政府都走數？"},{"pid":"80a48dec4ffd9df643d204a16727d09400615341","tid":1849400,"uid":117837,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"日文報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://article.yahoo.co.jp/detail/dc09199ce074e19bd4d8b20a1fccfc6f841b55e6?fbclid=IwAR23Cv2y_kN_kdrZ4rBU84921sWIkOE2Xc-nnZx90UczpP55_WW_PhGR9RU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farticle.yahoo.co.jp%2Fdetail%2Fdc09199ce074e19bd4d8b20a1fccfc6f841b55e6%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR23Cv2y_kN_kdrZ4rBU84921sWIkOE2Xc-nnZx90UczpP55_WW_PhGR9RU&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=0d6c5b33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://article.yahoo.co.jp/detail/dc09199ce074e19bd4d8b20a1fccfc6f841b55e6?fbclid=IwAR23Cv2y_kN_kdrZ4rBU84921sWIkOE2Xc-nnZx90UczpP55_WW_PhGR9RU</a>